In this situation we need to Adapt and over come. 

There is no reason why you can‚Äôt progress during this period. If not maintain. It‚Äôs all about your mentality and mind. If you want it. Get it. If you want to sit down and give up that is your choice.

There are many different training methods. Lots of different ways to progress. Look at switching up your training methods. Use super setting. Drop setting. Make sure you are burning those muscles out. Pushing yourself. If you dont have as heavy weight keep your reps high. Intensity high. And make sure your rest periods between your working sets shorter.

This is such a good time to be focusing on our form. How were executing our movements. Because we don‚Äôt have as heavier weights we have the opportunity to do so.
